                        <head><hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">Acting Secretary of
                                    State</gloss> to Minister <persName type="to">Rockhill</persName>.</hi></head>
                        <opener><seg rendition="#center">[Telegram—Paraphrase.]</seg></opener>
                        <opener><dateline rendition="#right"><placeName><hi rend="smallcaps">Department of State</hi>,<lb/><hi rend="italic">Washington</hi></placeName>, <hi rend="italic"><date calendar="gregorian" when="1906-09-27">September 27,
                                        1906</date></hi>.</dateline></opener>
                        <p>(Mr. Adee asks what action has been taken concerning customs at
                            Newchwang, in pursuance of department’s telegram of August 30.)</p>
